name: Conway-s-game-of-life
body:
### Welcome to the homepage of Android Version of Conway's Game of life.
The version of SDK I use is 11 and the instant apk can be installed only on platforms 3.0 and above.

### What to be expected
A two-player version game of life will be developed in one month.

### Support or Contact
Having trouble with this project? Mail to me and i will contact immediately.
